message.entry: First argument must be a scalar ThemeContainer.
A scalar GraphicsTheme object must be specified.
Theme name must be either "dark" or "light".
Argument must be a valid graphics object.
Too many input arguments. Specify one theme only.
{0} must be a non-zero-length scalar string or character vector.
Argument must be a 3-element numeric matrix convertible to an RGB color or the string "remove".
Cannot map the {0} property to the {1} attribute.
Input must be a visible, writable property of class {0}.
Reset the SeriesIndex property of {0} to an integer greater than zero to restore the default ColorOrder behavior.
All objects must be of the same class.
Argument must be a valid, themeable graphics object.
All objects must share the same figure ancestor, or be unparented.
This object does not support the 'remove' syntax for the {0} property.
